cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.IR 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on natural language processing tasks such as cloze-style reading comprehension on multiparty dialogue. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is also likely as the paper proposes deep learning models to validate the tasks. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper discusses the limitations of previous work and suggests new tasks for more comprehensive predictions. 
- cs.SD (Software Engineering) is less likely but still possible as the paper may discuss the implementation of the proposed tasks and models. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is also less likely but possible as the paper may discuss the retrieval of relevant information from the dialogue for the cloze-style reading comprehension tasks.
